  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>AddChildNode</TypeRef> method adds the specified <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderableNode">IRenderableNode</PageRef>
      to the list of child nodes.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void AddChildNode(IRenderableNode* childNode);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="IRenderableNode*!cobalt.graphics.IRenderableNode" Name="childNode">
          The <TypeRef>IRenderableNode</TypeRef> node to add to the list of child nodes
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
